{"tid":989118,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有人好容易會產生罪疚感？","createTime":"2019-01-20T15:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T15:44:30.000Z","uid":90457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14b425ff4551246810528e2ebf35755c4693ca9e","tid":989118,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:16:50.000Z","msg":"最近一單<br />\n<br />\n樓豬等巴士期間有兩姊妹喺附近追逐，兩個個樣望落應該未夠五歲<br />\n就這樣，其中一個應該係妹妹嚟，隻腳踢到我鞋邊，成個人仆落地面，手掌、面刮傷，爆哂缸，猛喺度喊<br />\n<br />\n而家諗，本來唔係我錯，意外冇人想發生，而且我一直都企定定，我隻腳都冇郁過，係佢自己踩埋嚟<br />\n<br />\n但嗰刻我第一個反應就係同佢哋同行嘅父母講對唔住（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），而且當時有個諗法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我唔係企喺呢個位，個妹妹唔會仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n即係話，眼見有啲乜嘢唔好嘅嘢發生咗，個腦裡面硬係喺度諗「如果唔係我，就唔會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"26f4d6136dd604ee4d02d7343489bef226cb30b9","tid":989118,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"仆吓街姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔洗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4662ab014c1e1752238b4fa8f38693061182ccd0","tid":989118,"uid":134549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:19:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e428872e67415da454c33d3d118a43f5296a6a1","tid":989118,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"太有同情心或者太易就覺得guilty唔係一件好事"},{"pid":"333048953de08447328b21a6f1e5d45ecf99ec38","tid":989118,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e428872e67415da454c33d3d118a43f5296a6a1","tid":989118,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"太有同情心或者太易就覺得guilty唔係一件好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"